data.description: This charming single-family ranch home welcomes you into a spacious foyer and to the left, a gracious dining room awaits, perfect for hosting intimate dinners or festive gatherings with friends and family. Beyond, an open concept design seamlessly connects the kitchen and family room, creating a warm and inviting space for everyday living and entertaining. Prepare culinary delights in the well-appointed kitchen (including gas appliances) while staying engaged with guests lounging in the family room a true hub of activity and connection.  Here, you'll also enjoy the gas fireplace making things cozy during those cold winter nights.  With the glass door exiting to the patio along with two walls of windows, you'll enjoy the beautiful natural light that fills the family room, and the vaulted ceilings add to the open visual appeal.  Retreat to the spacious primary bedroom where tranquility awaits. Enjoy the luxury of an ensuite bathroom and a sprawling walk-in closet, offering ample space to unwind and recharge after a long day.  Two additional bedrooms, thoughtfully designed and adorned with natural light, share a conveniently located hall bathroom, ensuring comfort and convenience for all occupants.  Outside your front door, lush wooded views provide a picturesque backdrop, inviting you to relax and reconnect with nature while the rear of the home features a patio that's perfect for enjoying outdoor dining and entertaining. Plus, as part of a coveted swim and tennis community, residents can indulge in endless recreation and leisure activities right at their fingertips.
